/target

# The guest program and verification keys are downloaded at build time by
# `build.rs` from the matching `zksync_airbender_verifier` release — never
# committed. The repo-wide .gitignore already excludes `dist`; we additionally
# exclude the downloaded VKs and the per-file `.tag` cache markers `build.rs`
# writes.
/vks/fri_vk.bin
/vks/snark_vk.json
/vks/*.tag
/guest/dist/app/*.tag
